sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FB as Formbricks<br/>Cloud Form
    participant NG as Ngrok<br/>Tunnel
    participant BE as Backend<br/>Express API
    participant DB as Database<br/>PostgreSQL
    participant Discord as Discord<br/>Bot Service
    participant Notif as Notifikasi<br/>Email dan N8N

    Note over FB, BE: User mengisi form Formbricks<br/>(Support ATAU Incident)

    FB ->> NG: POST payload + surveyId + questions
    activate NG
    NG ->> BE: Forward POST /webhook/formbricks
    deactivate NG
    activate BE

    BE ->> BE: parseFormbricksPayload (body)
    BE ->> BE: Deteksi surveyId - Support atau Incident
    BE ->> BE: Map field ID ke label via FIELD_MAP

    alt Validasi payload gagal
        BE -->> NG: 400 Bad Request
        NG -->> FB: Error - webhook failed
    else Payload valid
        BE ->> DB: submission.create (rawPayload)
        activate DB
        DB -->> BE: submission saved
        deactivate DB

        alt Survey = Form Tiket Support
            BE ->> BE: createTicket (type=SUPPORT,<br/>formId=formbricks_support)
        else Survey = Form Tiket Incident
            BE ->> BE: createTicket (type=INCIDENT,<br/>formId=formbricks_incident)
        end

        BE ->> BE: Classifier - classifyTicketFields
        BE ->> DB: ticket.create (ticketData)
        activate DB
        DB -->> BE: ticket id dan ticketNumber
        deactivate DB

        par Notifikasi Paralel
            BE ->> Discord: postTicketToChannel (ticket)
            activate Discord
            Discord -->> BE: threadId
            deactivate Discord
        and
            BE ->> Notif: sendConfirmation (email)
            activate Notif
            Notif -->> BE: Email + N8N triggered
            deactivate Notif
        end

        BE -->> NG: 200 OK - ticketId
        deactivate BE
        NG -->> FB: 200 OK (webhook delivered)
    end